00:32:27,727 --> 00:32:30,097
No one asked me, so I can't choose?

506
00:32:32,947 --> 00:32:35,797
They worked, so they get to choose.

507
00:32:35,797 --> 00:32:38,427
You didn't do any work. How about you do some work then?

508
00:32:38,427 --> 00:32:40,107
I'll work.

509
00:32:40,107 --> 00:32:41,497
Let's braise it then.

510
00:32:41,497 --> 00:32:44,777
Sure, I'll let you all taste my cooking.

511
00:32:44,777 --> 00:32:48,120
