519
00:33:16,947 --> 00:33:21,147
Looks like the story of a small-town girl and a top student wasn't just a rumor after all.

520
00:33:21,147 --> 00:33:22,927
I think you guys have something going on.

521
00:33:22,927 --> 00:33:24,787
You think about romance all day long.

522
00:33:24,787 --> 00:33:26,640
Your phone will be confiscated by the teacher soon.

523
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,920
- Stay out of this. 
 - What?

524
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,697
Sir, someone's playing with his phone!

525
00:33:29,697 --> 00:33:32,707
Keep your voice down, you four-eyed boy.

526
00:33:45,827 --> 00:33:47,297
Coming.

527
00:33:47,297 --> 00:33:51,387
Students, let's play a round after dinner.

528
00:33:51,387 --> 00:33:52,627
I'm not playing.

529
00:33:52,627 --> 00:33:55,497
I'm not playing. I think we should take a nap and rest after eating.

530
00:33:55,497 --> 00:33:58,347
I'm not asking you to play poker. We're playing truth or dare.

531
00:33:58,347 --> 00:33:59,797
- No. 
 - Just draw one.

532
00:33:59,797 --> 00:34:02,460
Whoever got the smallest card loses. Let's play.

533
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,217
- After-meal entertainment. 
 - Let's play for a while.

534
00:34:04,217 --> 00:34:05,897
- Have some fun. 
 - Let's play.

535
00:34:05,897 --> 00:34:07,407
Hurry.

536
00:34:10,827 --> 00:34:12,017
Sorry, everyone.

537
00:34:12,017 --> 00:34:13,177
I need to go to the toilet.

538
00:34:13,177 --> 00:34:14,747
Go.

539
00:34:14,747 --> 00:34:16,297
Come on.

540
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:20,235
- Yours is the smallest. 
 - Whose card is the smallest?

541
00:34:20,235 --> 00:34:21,947
Your card is the smallest.

542
00:34:23,307 --> 00:34:27,840
- Ask away. 
 - If you could choose your own desk mate,

543
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,907
who in our class would you pick?

544
00:34:29,907 --> 00:34:31,597
Cong, of course.

545
00:34:31,597 --> 00:34:33,537
Tell the truth or I'll punish you.

546
00:34:33,537 --> 00:34:34,727
I'm telling the truth.

547
00:34:34,727 --> 00:34:36,307
Can't you see how close we are?

548
00:34:36,307 --> 00:34:38,307
Fine, let me rephrase.

549
00:34:38,307 --> 00:34:41,550
If you had to choose a girl as your desk mate, who would you choose?

550
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:44,457
That's your second question. I haven't lost yet. Hurry, put it down.

551
00:34:44,457 --> 00:34:46,097
Sure. Don't play dirty.

552
00:34:46,097 --> 00:34:48,217
Look at this guy, trying to cheat!

553
00:34:53,107 --> 00:34:56,097
- Your card is still the smallest. 
 - You again.

554
00:34:56,097 --> 00:34:57,360
You...

555
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:59,127
How can it be, really?

556
00:34:59,127 --> 00:35:00,497
- Don't play dirty. 
 - I didn't.

557
00:35:00,497 --> 00:35:01,537
Don't play dirty.

558
00:35:01,537 --> 00:35:03,097
Accept defeat.

559
00:35:03,097 --> 00:35:04,887
Why are you causing a ruckus?

560
00:35:04,887 --> 00:35:06,617
- Speak. 
 - Hurry.

561
00:35:07,827 --> 00:35:11,017
I really don't have anyone I especially want to sit next to.

562
00:35:11,017 --> 00:35:13,387
You must choose one.

563
00:35:13,387 --> 00:35:15,387
You then.

564
00:35:15,387 --> 00:35:16,597
Xin Yan.

565
00:35:16,597 --> 00:35:19,027
All right, next round.

566
00:35:23,547 --> 00:35:25,297
Here.

567
00:35:26,827 --> 00:35:28,137
Come on, play your cards.

568
00:35:28,137 --> 00:35:31,377
Here, three, two, one. Who is it?

569
00:35:31,377 --> 00:35:33,427
Chen Huan Er.

570
00:35:33,427 --> 00:35:36,609
- If it's Huan Er, I'll ask something simple. 
 - Why?

571
00:35:36,609 --> 00:35:37,680
You ask her.

572
00:35:37,680 --> 00:35:39,427
I'll ask.

573
00:35:39,427 --> 00:35:41,267
Chen Huan Er,

574
00:35:41,267 --> 00:35:46,397
who do you admire most in our class?

575
00:35:52,387 --> 00:35:54,487
I pick Song Cong.

576
00:36:00,420 --> 00:36:02,127
What are you guys talking about? You're so excited.

577
00:36:02,127 --> 00:36:05,177
- Chen Huan Er said... 
 - Nothing.

578
00:36:05,177 --> 00:36:08,167
Song Cong, we haven't seen your card.

579
00:36:08,167 --> 00:36:09,727
- Take it out and show us. 
 - Yes.

580
00:36:12,137 --> 00:36:13,497
Your card is the smallest.

581
00:36:13,497 --> 00:36:15,497
I... I have to ask you a question.

582
00:36:15,497 --> 00:36:17,873
Who do you admire most in our class?

583
00:36:17,873 --> 00:36:19,307
Don't ask the same questions.

584
00:36:19,307 --> 00:36:21,747
- How boring. 
 - This question is fun.

585
00:36:21,747 --> 00:36:24,407
Didn't you just go to the bathroom? Why are you going again?

586
00:36:32,577 --> 00:36:37,177
Sorry, everyone. My stomach is really upset today.

587
00:36:37,177 --> 00:36:38,947
I don't have any tissues.

588
00:36:38,947 --> 00:36:40,177
Does anyone have some?

589
00:36:40,177 --> 00:36:42,757
I didn't bring any.

590
00:36:42,757 --> 00:36:44,607
I'll go get some for you.

591
00:36:44,607 --> 00:36:46,007
Sure.

592
00:36:47,152 --> 00:36:48,560
What's wrong with you?

593
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,657
- I don't know. 
 - Cong, why don't you go first?

594
00:36:50,657 --> 00:36:53,807
We'll have Jing Xi Chi bring it to you later.

595
00:36:53,807 --> 00:36:56,177
- Thank you. 
 - Go.

596
00:37:03,787 --> 00:37:07,627
Cong said his stomach hurt and went back to the dorm to lie down.

597
00:37:09,617 --> 00:37:12,347
You didn't really poison him, did you?

598
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:17,137
What are you talking about? How come we're fine? Don't scare Huan Er.

599
00:37:17,137 --> 00:37:19,680
I'll go to the fields to see if there's any sweet potato root.

600
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:21,617
It can stop diarrhea when soaked in hot water.

601
00:37:21,617 --> 00:37:23,347
Sweet potato root?

602
00:37:23,347 --> 00:37:25,657
You'd better not make it worse.

603
00:37:25,657 --> 00:37:28,427
It'll work. My grandpa was a traditional medicine practitioner.

604
00:37:28,427 --> 00:37:31,787
When I had a stomachache, he soaked it in hot water and made me drink it.

605
00:37:31,787 --> 00:37:34,617
If you add copper leaf herb and Ailanthus root,

606
00:37:34,617 --> 00:37:36,507
these three ingredients together will work.

607
00:37:36,507 --> 00:37:37,947
Let's go.

608
00:37:46,307 --> 00:37:49,537
Chen Huan Er, did you find any?

609
00:37:49,537 --> 00:37:51,787
- No. 
 - Still nothing?

610
00:37:51,787 --> 00:37:54,497
You're so slow.

611
00:37:54,497 --> 00:37:56,407
Are these enough?

612
00:37:56,407 --> 00:37:58,537
What are these?

613
00:37:58,537 --> 00:38:01,347
Sweet potato root. The place is full of them.

614
00:38:01,347 --> 00:38:03,347
Aren't these sweet potatoes?

615
00:38:03,347 --> 00:38:05,907
Yeah, sweet potato roots.

616
00:38:05,907 --> 00:38:07,347
This is the root. Sweet potato root.

617
00:38:07,347 --> 00:38:10,737
Sweet potato root isn't the root of a sweet potato.

618
00:38:12,387 --> 00:38:15,280
Sweet potato root isn't the root of a sweet potato?

619
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,457
Chen Huan Er, why don't you listen to yourself?

620
00:38:17,457 --> 00:38:21,227
Sweet potato root isn't the root of a sweet potato. Did you hear that?

621
00:38:21,227 --> 00:38:22,700
- Sweet potato root isn't... 
 - Sweet potato root.

622
00:38:22,700 --> 00:38:26,057
Wait. Sweet potato root isn't the root...

623
00:38:26,057 --> 00:38:29,777
Sweet potato root is actually the name of a herb.

624
00:38:31,427 --> 00:38:36,197
Xi Chi, sweet potato is already a root tuber.

625
00:38:38,977 --> 00:38:40,347
A root tuber?

626
00:38:40,347 --> 00:38:41,867
Let's roast this and eat it tonight.

627
00:38:41,867 --> 00:38:43,907
It should be tasty.

628
00:38:43,907 --> 00:38:46,867
Sweet potato root isn't the root of a sweet potato.

629
00:38:46,867 --> 00:38:50,457
Sweet potato root isn't the root of a sweet potato.

630
00:38:50,457 --> 00:38:52,137
Jing Xi Chi.

631
00:38:52,137 --> 00:38:55,167
Chen Huan Er is so anxious to find medicine for Song Cong.

632
00:38:55,167 --> 00:38:57,840
Are they that close?

633
00:38:57,840 --> 00:39:00,980
What nonsense are you talking about? We're sworn brothers.

634
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:06,617
If you have time to gossip about others, why don't you help me find the sweet potato root?

635
00:39:06,617 --> 00:39:09,747
Sure, I'll help.

636
00:39:09,747 --> 00:39:12,537
But isn't this the plot of a Chinese fantasy drama?

637
00:39:12,537 --> 00:39:17,017
The little pharmacist would dig three feet to find the herb to save the celestial being.

638
00:39:17,017 --> 00:39:19,787
In the end, he still has to rely on me to save him.

639
00:39:19,787 --> 00:39:21,137
Chen Huan Er!

640
00:39:21,137 --> 00:39:23,360
Sweet potato root!

641
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:25,182
Are you sure it's sweet potato root?

642
00:39:25,182 --> 00:39:28,440
Sweet potato root. The sweet potato root! The herb!

643
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:31,137
- Are you sure it's sweet potato root? 
 - It's sweet potato root.

644
00:39:31,137 --> 00:39:32,747
You mean it's that herb?

645
00:39:32,747 --> 00:39:34,457
Look at the root. This root.

646
00:39:34,457 --> 00:39:35,927
It's true.

647
00:39:35,927 --> 00:39:37,737
Amazing.

648
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:49,017
Cong said he wants a hot water bottle. Does anyone have one?

649
00:39:49,017 --> 00:39:51,427
Go grab one from my dorm. It's on the bed.

650
00:39:51,427 --> 00:39:53,427
You really have everything. I'll go then.

651
00:39:53,427 --> 00:39:54,987
Bye.

