00:40:42,657 --> 00:40:45,017
Where else can I get you this hot water bottle?

665
00:40:45,017 --> 00:40:47,747
We just got back from digging up a herb for you.

666
00:40:47,747 --> 00:40:50,907
Actually, Chen Huan Er is really good.

667
00:40:50,907 --> 00:40:53,567
She's pretty knowledgeable about medicinal herbs.

668
00:40:53,567 --> 00:40:55,360
But man, that root was such a pain to dig up.

669
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:58,736
Do you know that sweet potato root isn't actually the root of a sweet potato?

670
00:40:58,736 --> 00:41:01,577
Do you get it? What's the use of her knowing so much?

